smartcard.ulist.ulist

class documentation

class ulist(list):

Known subclasses: smartcard.reader.ReaderGroups.innerreadergroups

View In Hierarchy

ulist ensures that all items are unique and provides an __onadditem__ hook to perform custom action in subclasses.
